{'Score': 'N/A', 'feedback': 'Insufficient evidence to evaluate', 'score_explanation': 'No specific tasks or deadlines discussed.'}, 'Attention to Detail': {'Score': 8, 'feedback': 'Detailed design knowledge', 'score_explanation': 'Comprehensive understanding of design tools and features.'}}, 'Summary': 'The candidate demonstrated strong skills in UI design and tool usage, with an impressive 90% in both Introduction and Photoshop, and a perfect 100% in Figma. Their understanding of C was mixed, with a perfect score in one instance but a complete lack of implementation in another, resulting in an average score of 50%. Testing and Project categories both scored 50%, indicating a basic understanding but lacking depth and specific details. Manual testing was slightly below average at 50%, showing a need for more detailed criteria and handling steps. Overall, the candidate excels in design tools but needs improvement in testing methodologies and C programming consistency.', 'Strengths': "The candidate's strengths lie in UI design and tool proficiency, scoring 90% in both Introduction and Photoshop, and achieving a perfect 100% in Figma. Their ability to articulate their skills and experience clearly is also a notable strength.", 'Weaknesses': "The candidate's weaknesses are evident in testing and C programming, with both areas scoring 50%. They need to deepen their understanding of testing methodologies and ensure consistent implementation in C programming tasks.", 'MandatorySkillScore': None, 'OverAllScore': '6.8', 'OverAllCommunicationScore': '6.0', 'OverAllAiUsagePercentage': '29.2', 'OverAllAuthenticityPercentage': '70.8', 'OverAllAuthenticityText': 'high', 'OverAllAuthenticityColor': 'green', 'OverAllAiUsageText': 'low'}, 'statusCode': 200}
