': 'N/A', 'feedback': 'Insufficient evidence to evaluate', 'score_explanation': 'No specific evidence on time management.'}, 'Attention to Detail': {'Score': 9, 'feedback': 'Accurate in Figma and Photoshop', 'score_explanation': 'High accuracy in design tool usage.'}}, 'Summary': "The candidate demonstrated strong skills in Figma and Photoshop, scoring 100% and 90% respectively, showcasing proficiency in design tools. Their introduction was effective at 80%, highlighting relevant skills in UI design. However, their performance in testing and project categories was moderate, both at 50%, indicating a need for deeper understanding and specific methodologies in these areas. Manual testing also showed room for improvement with a score of 55%, lacking detailed criteria for decision-making. The candidate's performance in C was inconsistent, with a perfect score in one instance but a complete miss in another, averaging 50% overall.", 'Strengths': 'The candidate excelled in Figma and Photoshop, achieving 100% and 90% respectively, indicating strong design tool proficiency. Their introduction was also solid at 80%, effectively highlighting their skills in UI design and multimedia editing.', 'Weaknesses': 'The candidate needs improvement in testing and project areas, both at 50%, lacking depth and specific methodologies. Manual testing at 55% requires more detailed criteria. In C, inconsistent performance was noted, with a perfect score offset by a complete miss.', 'MandatorySkillScore': None, 'OverAllScore': '6.8', 'OverAllCommunicationScore': '7.0', 'OverAllAiUsagePercentage': '30.2', 'OverAllAuthenticityPercentage': '69.8', 'OverAllAuthenticityText': 'medium', 'OverAllAuthenticityColor': 'orange', 'OverAllAiUsageText': 'low'}, 'statusCode': 200}
